{
  "info": {
    "name": "Didegan Platform - Web API Gateway",
    "description": "Complete API collection for the Didegan/MembersFactory platform.\n\nBase URL: {{baseUrl}}/api/v1\n\n## Authentication\nAll authenticated endpoints require a Bearer token in the Authorization header.\n1. Register or login via /auth/register or /auth/login\n2. Use the returned accessToken as the Bearer token\n3. When the token expires, use /auth/refresh with the refreshToken to get a new pair\n\n## Modules\n- **Auth** - Registration, login, Telegram Mini App auth, profile management\n- **Advertiser Wallet** - TON wallet, deposits, balance, transactions\n- **Advertiser Campaigns** - Create/manage member acquisition campaigns\n- **Publisher Platforms** - Register and manage advertising bot platforms\n- **Publisher Earnings** - Track earnings, withdraw funds\n- **Publisher Custom Campaigns** - Register custom campaigns\n- **Content Bots** - AI-powered auto-posting bots for channels\n- **Subscriptions** - Content bot subscription packages\n- **Merchant Wallet** - Merchant TON wallet and deposits\n- **Marketplace** - Buy/sell Telegram channels and groups",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "12345678"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3001",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "accessToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "refreshToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
